trans-unit.source: Represents the collection of Response Headers as defined in RFC 2616.
trans-unit.target: 代表回應標頭的集合，如 RFC 2616 中所定義。

trans-unit.source: This type is derived from <xref:System.Net.Http.Headers.HttpHeaders>.
trans-unit.target: 此類型衍生自<xref:System.Net.Http.Headers.HttpHeaders>。

trans-unit.source: Gets the value of the <see langword="Accept-Ranges" /> header for an HTTP response.
trans-unit.target: 取得 HTTP 回應的 <see langword="Accept-Ranges" /> 標頭值。

trans-unit.source: The value of the <see langword="Accept-Ranges" /> header for an HTTP response.
trans-unit.target: HTTP 回應的 <see langword="Accept-Ranges" /> 標頭值。
